Build-Depends: debhelper
Standards-Version: 3.0.0

Package: cloudwatchd
Version: 3
Architecture: all
Depends: python, python-boto
Replaces: cloudwatchd
Description: Continuously stream a directory of script output(s) to Amazon's Cloudwatch
 A daemon which takes a directory of scripts in various programming languages,
 runs them at a designated interval, and sends their stdout along with parsed
 metadata to Amazon's Cloudwatch.
